# 5. Configure proper database connection pooling
# 6. Set up monitoring and alerting for production issues
# 7. Enable HTTPS and set proper security headers
# 8. Configure proper backup and recovery procedures
# 9. Update all calendar IDs with your actual GHL calendar IDs
# 10. Configure AWS S3 bucket policies and ClamAV scanner for document security
# 11. Set up proper Google Maps API restrictions for security
# 12. Configure feature flags based on your deployment requirements 